These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, pear, papaya, pomegranate, raspberry, cucumber, plum
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, skydiving, puzzles, filmmaking, traveling, card-games, fishing
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
11. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the person eating papaya is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Food   | raspberry      | papaya      | cucumber    | plum    | pear | cranberry     | pomegranate     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | traveling | puzzles | reading | card-games   | fishing | skydiving |

