.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, polish, thai, chinese, indian, pakistani, turkish
There 7 different types of food: tomato, apricot, lemon, grapes, blueberry, onion, cauliflower
 1. the thai is on the left or right of the polish##3
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 3. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
 4. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
 5. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating onion is the chinese##1
 7. the polish is the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the chinese is the person eating onion##1
10. the thai is between the person eating onion and the polish##2
11. the pakistani is in the middle##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
13. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
14. the turkish is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Nationality   | polish   | thai | chinese | pakistani   | turkish | russian | indian |
| Food           | blueberry | tomato          | onion    | apricot | grapes     | lemon      | cauliflower    |

