.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, classical, dubstep, trance, blues, hip-hop, folk
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian, russian, australian, italian, indian, colombian
 1. the russian is on the right of the colombian##1
 2. the colombian is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 4. the fan of classical is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of trance##2
 5. the indian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 6. the russian is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the italian is in an odd position##4
 8. the canadian is on the far left##1
 9. the nigerian is the fan of funk##1
10. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
11. the indian is the fan of folk##1
12. the italian is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Music-Genre   | trance        | classical  | hip-hop | dubstep | blues           | folk           | funk  |
| Nationality    | canadian | australian | colombian   | russian    | italian | indian | nigerian |

