 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
 5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 8. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
11. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
