.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, juice, soy-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
City: berlin, miami, hannover, rome, london, new-york, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to miami and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 5. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 6. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is the person traveling to hannover##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
11. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
12. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
13. the person traveling to new-york is the person drinking juice##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
15. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5     |  6   |    7     |
| Beverage          | soy-milk | iced-tea | coffee | water | hot-chocolate | juice | mirinda |
| City   | hannover   | london      | rome     | liverpool    | berlin | new-york  | miami      |

