10. the person who growsorchid is between the person watching scientific movies and the person who growsaconite##2
11. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Flower   | iris     | aconite   | orchid      | amaryllis | balloon-flower    | sunflower | poppy |
| Movie-Genre       | documentary | time-travel | crime | scientific  | adventure | western     | spy    |

