.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, havana, swisher, game, davidoff, old-henry
7 different games are played: whist, snooker, scrabble, chess, bridge, canasta, poker
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 3. the person playing bridge is the old-henry-smoker##1
 4. the person playing poker is the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the game-smoker is the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing chess is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
12. the swisher-smoker is in an odd position##4
13. the person playing bridge is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
14. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar          | swisher  | ritmeester | montecristo     | old-henry  | havana | davidoff    | game  |
| Game   | chess | canasta  | whist | bridge | snooker | poker | scrabble |

