.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, january, november, september, june, march, july
There are 7 different favourite colors: red, azure, grey, ivory, aquamarine, blood-red, white
 1. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes azure##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who likes white##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
12. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Birthday          | march   | november | july | april | june | january | september |
| Color   | aquamarine | white      | blood-red     | grey  | ivory | red         | azure    |

 